INSERT INTO `field_body` (`pages_id`, `data`) VALUES('1001', '<p>I am an application developer, with good experience on XHTML/CSS, JavaScript (Dojo and jQuery) , Java, C# ASP.NET MVC 3,  PHP/Zend framework 2 and Yii Framework and also worked a lot with WordPress (Plugins,Caching and Extending WordPress Applications) , I also work as a contract Web developer to some companies, I give consultations on Web Development, Moodle Customization, Optimization of existing websites and ways to make Web Application user friendly. I occasionally branch of from Web Development to try other techs like am eager to learn 3D on Web and Game Development.</p>\n\n<h2>A brief History about me</h2>\n\n<p>I use to work at Linkeo Web Agencie, a French ICT company in Mauritius Quatre Bornne. Despite being a PHP/JS Developer I am quite versed with C#, Java ( J2ME and Android API, Processing) I try to learn as much as I can. Currently I left Leaps and Bounds for Interswitch Nigeria Limited where I am a Software Developer, where I work on .. (Confidential). I spend most of my time researching on Gaming and game development and creating modules for open source projects anything but Wordpress.</p>\n\n<h3>Frontend Web Development Tools</h3>\n\n<ul><li>IDE / Text Editors (Eclipse Zend, Aptana Studio and Sublime Text Editor 3)</li>\n	<li>Emmet (HTML markup/ CSS Generation)</li>\n	<li>LESS (CSS Preprocessor) I can’t imagine writing CSS again without these</li>\n	<li>JavaScript (Jquery, Dojotoolkit (90% of the time))</li>\n	<li>Maqetta</li>\n	<li>HTML5 Mobile Web Development (Dojotoolkit,jQuery)</li>\n</ul><h3>Backend Web Development Tools</h3>\n\n<ul><li>PHP Frameworks (Zend 2, Yii,ImpressPages )</li>\n	<li>Composer/PHPUnit</li>\n	<li>VLE (Moodle)</li>\n	<li>WordPress</li>\n</ul><h3>Others</h3>\n\n<ul><li>Game Development (Phaser, Processing)</li>\n	<li>ASP.NET MVC 3</li>\n	<li>C#/Java (Intermediate)</li>\n	<li>GNU/Linux</li>\n</ul>');
